item.dc:creator: @Swift1 Swift`
item.description:
@Swift1 wrote:

Right click your run.bat and change the numbers:

You should see something like this

"C:\Program Files\Java\jdk\x.x.x_xx

Change the x’s for your JDK version, probably

"C:\Program Files\Java\jdk\1.6.0_07

My compiler for example, looks like this (wont help much though):

@echo off cd ../src echo Compiling net.com.swift.net.codec "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_07\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../build/ ./net/com/swift/net/codec/*.java echo Compiling net.com.espeon "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_07\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../build/ ./net/com/swift/*.java echo Compiling net.com.espeon.model "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_07\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../build/ ./net/com/swift/model/*.java echo Compiling net.com.swift.model.update "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_07\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../build/ ./net/com/swift/model/update/*.java echo Compiling net.com.swift.model.items "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_07\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../build/ ./net/com/swift/model/items/*.java echo Compiling net.com.swift.model.misc "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_07\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../build/ ./net/com/swift/model/misc/*.java echo Compiling net.com.swift.model.combat "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_07\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../build/ ./net/com/swift/model/combat/*.java echo Compiling net.com.swift.io "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_07\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../build/ ./net/com/swift/io/*.java echo Compiling net.com.swift.io.packethandler "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_07\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../build/ ./net/com/swift/net/packethandler/*.java echo Compiling net.com.swift.net "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_07\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../build/ ./net/com/swift/net/*.java echo Compiling net.com.swift.util "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_07\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../build/ ./net/com/swift/util/*.java echo Compiling net.com.swift.world.mapdata "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_07\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../build/ ./net/com/swift/world/mapdata/*.java echo Compiling net.com.swift.world.items "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_07\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../build/ ./net/com/swift/world/items/*.java pause
